$lang['The hexadecimal system is a base 16 number notation, while the decimal system is a base 10 number notation. In other words, the hexadecimal system uses 16 symbols to represent numbers, while the decimal system uses 10 symbols. This expansion also allows for a higher information density-hexadecimal digits can represent twice as many values as decimal digits.'] = 'Sistèm egzadesimal la se yon notasyon nimewo baz 16, pandan y ap sistèm desimal la se yon notasyon nimewo baz 10. Nan lòt mo, sistèm egzadesimal la sèvi ak 16 senbòl pou reprezante nimewo, alòske sistèm desimal la sèvi ak 10 senbòl. Ekspansyon sa a pèmèt tou pou yon enfòmasyon ki pi wo dansite-chif egzadesimal ka reprezante de fwa plis valè pase chif desimal.';
